programme.title: Bidadari: Sara Kirana Ep1
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Maisarah, isteri yang patuh dan taat pada suaminya, Zulfakar dicerai tanpa sebab. Sara yang kecewa, bangkit semula sebagai Sara Kirana, seorang penulis novel. Dia dibantu oleh Zahrin, adik Zulfakar yang selama ini menyimpan hati kepadanya. Cinta mula berpaut, namun percintaan mereka mendapat tentangan dari bekas mentuanya, Puan Zulaikha dan Haji Salam yang tidak bersetuju kerana dianggap kurang manis memandangkan Zulfakar masih hidup. Namun kerana sayangkan anak, mereka menerima Maisarah sekali lagi menjadi menantu. Selepas mereka berkahwin, Zulfakar cuba mendekati Maisarah kembali. Perkahwinan barunya dengan Elly tidak bahagia. Zahrin mula cemburu akan abangnya. Malang tak berbau, tiba-tiba Zahrin ditimpa kemalangan dan terlantar koma. Pelakon: Mia Ahmad, Hafreez Adam, Jaslin Puasa, Eyka Farhana, Akmal Ahmad, Kuza, dan Rahhim Omar.

programme.desc: Adina telah mula bekerja di syarikat Aiman dan Noah pula telah dilantik secara rasmi sebagai CEO Orkids Holding. Mengendalikan syarikat yang mengalami masalah kewangan sememangnya menuntut sepenuh perhatian untuk memulihkannya, sekali gus menambah baik prestasi syarikat. Pun begitu, liku hidup yang terpaksa ditempuhi Raudhah tidak semudah disangka apabila dia turut berdepan konflik dengan anak tirinya, Mazli, Suzi dan Dahlia yang begitu memusuhi dirinya.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep27
programme.desc: Selepas bertemu Serdar di Gcek, Ezgi dan zgr mula berfikir tentang apa yang perlu dilakukan apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Serdar juga akan menghadiri majlis perkahwinan Ebru. Rakan-rakan mereka cuba mencari idea dan membantu mereka untuk meneruskan perkahwinan. Sementara itu, Sevim dan Nevin bergaul dengan baik, dan dengan bimbingan Fitnat, mereka mula merancang untuk mengatasi Ezgi dan zgr. Ezgi dan zgr juga berpura-pura tidak sesuai antara satu sama lain agar tidak menyusahkan keluarga mereka. Ini membuatkan keluarga mereka sangsi dengan perkahwinan mereka berdua.

programme.title: Dia Neng Luar Biasa
programme.desc: Munirah (27 tahun) terpaksa mencari pekerjaan sesegera yang mungkin memandangkan duit simpanannya baru sahaja habis di gunakan untuk bercuti luar negara dan kebetulan belaku perselisihan salah faham antara dia dan majikanya yang menyebabkan dia diberhentikan kerja serta merta. Bagi menampung perbelanjaannya di ibu kota, Munirah mencari kerja kosong dan dia tertarik dengan satu iklan pembantu rumah disebuah rumah banglo mewah dimana, dia ditawarkan gaji yang lumayan. Namun Munirah tidak mengetahui banglo itu milik milik majikan lama yang memecat iaitu Dato Malek (37 tahun). Munirah mengambil kesempatan itu, untuk membalas dendam terhadap Dato Malek . Munirah menyamar sebagai pembantu Indonesia. Pelbagai usaha yang dilakukan oleh Munirah untuk mengenakan Dato Malek. Munirah masih tidak dapat melupakan saat dia dipecat dihadapan semua rakan sekerja yang lain hanya kerana salah faham yang belaku antara dia dengan Ati yang terkenal sebagai kaki kipas bos dan akhirnya setelah pelbagai rancangan yang Munirah rancangkan berakhir dengan Munirah menjadi isteri Dato Malek dan mereka saling jatuh cinta.

programme.title: Saat Hati Telah Memilih Ep14

Dia memberi tahu ke Haris jika papanya sudah menyetujui dia menikah dengan Andi. Sementara itu Haris juga memberi tahu ke Riri jika dia juga akan menikah dengan Tanti.

programme.title: Cinta Tanpa Henti Ep05
programme.desc: Maya terdengar apa yang diperkatakan Zakiah kepada Zarif. Dia tidak menyangka Zarif bertindak sedemikian. Bahkan Tan Sri Zaid juga sangat marah dan menasihati Zarif untuk menjaga nama baiknya. Zarif merasa tertekan kerana semua orang sedang menyalahkannya atas perbuatan yang dia tak lakukan. Namun ibunya Pn Sri Rosita tidak percaya Zarif melakukan hal itu. Dia segera minta Mak Hawa pisahkan hubungan Maya dan Hisyam kerana Zarif akan bertunang dengan Maya tidak lama lagi. Zarif tertekan dan ditenangkan oleh Hajar. Hajar ambil kesempatan membawa Zarif yang mabuk bermalam di rumahnya. Keesokannya Maya datang ke rumah Hajar terkejut melihat mereka tidur berdua-duaan. Zarif cuba menafikan bahawa dia tidak tahu apa yang telah berlaku. Hajar berbohong menyalahkan Zarif yang menidurinya. Hajar minta maaf pada Maya, Maya tidak kisah hubungannya dengan Zarif tetapi marah kerana melakukan maksiat. Maya berjaya memujuk Hisyam yang cuba jauhkan diri darinya. Dia bawa Hisyam pulang ke rumah dan makan bersama keluarga tetapi Rahim hanya memberi sindiran pedas. Keluarga Rahim sangat gembira mendapat berita Sally hamil. Hajar mahu pastikan Maya dapat bersama Hisyam kerana dia mahukan Zarif. Hajar kononnya simpati dengan Maya cuba beri idea untuk selamatkan hubungannya dengan Hisyam. Satu hari, seluruh keluarga terkejut apabila Maya beritahu bahawa dia hamil.

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep13
programme.desc: Memaparkan Melissa kini tahu perancangan puan Sarah yang telah umum pertunangan antara Syakir dengan Engku Melissa. Melissa juga tahu dan tidak berang, malah meminta Syakir jangan berdekatan dan berbual dengannya terutama ketika puan Sarah belum berlepas. Sebelum puan Sarah pulang, dia meminta Melissa lakukan segala pembersihan perlu terutama mengemas dapur, Melissa akur. Di rumah, Nora perasan yang Syakir memandang Melissa dan Melissa agak terkejut tetapi tenang apabila puan Sarah umumkan. Suaminya tidak perasan tetapi jika benar berlaku tentunya Syakir memberitahunya. Tuan Suhaimi menegur isterinya yang kelihatan riang, selamba menjawab puan Sarah kerana satu kerja telah selesai. Cuma tuan Suhaimi akui tidak semestinya Syakir setuju kerana dia tidak dimaklumkan. Tuan Suhaimi juga menyatakan Syakir tidak membantah kerana menjaga air muka orang tua. Dalam pada itu Syakir menegur Melissa yang bertungkus lumus dan dia meminta Melissa berhenti dan rehat sert tidur. Melissa pula terus tetap dengan panggilan tuan Syak kepada Syakir, ditegur Syakir tetapi Melissa telah menyatakan dia telah biasa. Syakir akan menjelaskan segala-galanya pada keesokannya. Esoknya Syakir telah sedia sarapan pagi, Melissa letih dan tertidur, malah Syakir lakukan segala kerja bersih hingga selesai. Dalam pada itu Syakir hanya berjumpa Jenny seperti kelaziman, meluahkan segala apa yang dia bermasalah sekarang. Apa pun terjadi, Syakir akui akan terus mempertahanan Melissa walaupun agak sukar untuk menentang atau berterus terang bimbangkan kesihatan ibunya. Dalam pada itu sepupu Melissa yang balik ke kampung memaklumkan hubungan antara Melissa dan Syakir begitu baik. Lalu ibu Melissa rasa lega dan meminta jikanya berjumpa Melissa, mintakan Syakir membawa kedua ibu dan bapanya, paling kurang untuk berbincang bagi majlis ringkas sebagai mewar-warkan mereka telah berkahwin. Di hari lain sepupu Melissa sampaikan hasrat ibu Melissa, Melissa terdiam sekejap tetapi seolah-olah tenang dan akui dia akan berbincang dengan Syakir. Kini Kamelia kelihatan agak gembira, tetapi Zamer yang sentiasa menemaninya berharap waspada kerana Melissa yang kelihatan pernah bersama Syakir, kini ada di rumah Syakir. Dalam pertemuan antara Syakir dan Kamelia sekali lagi Syakir anggapkan mereka sebagai rakan sahaja. Kamelia secara biasa, mengesyorkan apa salahnya jika mereka bersama, lagi pun ibunya sangat mengharapkan. Puan Sarah datang lagi dengan mengejut ke rumah anak menantunya. Dia menegur Melissa membawa sepupu ke dalam rumah, dia juga menegur Melissa basuhkan bajunya sendiri bersekali dengan baju Syakir. Dalam pada itu Engku Razi yang berbincang hal Syakir dan Kamelia, Engku Razi sekali lagi meminta ibunya mengingati reaksi dan muka Syakir apabila ibunya umumkan. Ibunya hanya andaikan pandangan itu sebagai pandangan peribadi Engku Razi, sebaliknya ibunya tahu yang Engku Razi pula meminati orang gaji Syakir(Melissa). Engku Razi pula menafikannya. Lantaran itu ibunya memuji Razi kerana kelak maruah keluarganya akan jatuh. Syakir sekali lagi bergeseran dengan ibunya dan sekali menegaskan dia tidak mahu kahwin dengan Kamelia. Syakir balik ke rumahnya, dia kesudahan dengan ibunya. Ketika bersama Kamelia Syakir sekali lagi memaklumkan hasrat ibunya, ibunya juga ada sakit jantung, jadi Syakir berjanji masih tidak sesuai untuk berterus terang. Sekali lagi meyakinkan Melissa yang antara mereka berdua akan sehidup semati. Melissa juga sedih akan hal tugas Syakir akan ke Kazakastan, tetapi redza. Di hari lain puan Sarah meminta pemandunya menjemput Melissa dan kemudiannya dia di arah untuk membeli belah untuk persiapan "hi-tea", Zaker cuba menganggunya, mujur Razi datang, Razi mengambil kesempatan hantar Melissa dan luahkan perasaannya kepada Melissa.

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep15
programme.desc: Normah berteriak mengetahui Jalal menikahi Kiah. Airil dan Norlin juga terkejut. Sementara itu, Jalal kelihatan sangat bahagia dengan Kiah. Normah berkurung dan meratap dalam bilik. Puas anak-anak memujuknya. Airil akhirnya dapat menerima kenyataan itu. Sofea pula rela menjadi tempat luahan kekusutan Airil. Norlin memperkenalkan Zamir kepada orang tuanya tetapi malu mulut ibunya masih celupar. Isteri Nizam, Rugayah mendapat tahu suaminya ingin melamar Fatihah. Dia bertemu Fatihah dan memberi amaran kepadanya. Hafiz menasihati Fatihah agar berhenti kerja tapi Fatihah mahu bertahan. Aleya yang terabai, sudah pandai ponteng sekolah. Fatihah mengamuk, Aleya merajuk dan lari ke rumah Kak Nor. Airil pulang sekali lagi ke kampung untuk nasihatkan ibunya, tetapi Normah asyik memfitnah ayahnya dengan Kiah. Farah terkejut apabila doktor mengesahkan dia hamil. Lebih membuatkan dia teruja apabila permohonannya untuk melanjutkan pengajian di peringkat Master juga diluluskan. Dalam teruja, hatinya tetap berbelah bahagi apabila memikirkan Zahin. Lukman pula disyaki terlibat dalam kehilangan wang syarikat.

programme.title: Rembat
programme.desc: Malik dan Chin Chye yang bertembung secara tidak sengaja. Namun satu malapetaka yang berlaku membuatkan mereka mengejar masa untuk ke peringkat akhir perlawanan bola sepak yang akan berlangsung kerana Chin Chye telah berjanji dengan ah long untuk memberi rasuah kepada pasukan Malaysia agar mereka kalah dalam perlawanan di antaraHarimau MalayadanThailand.Walaupun Malik tidak mahu melibatkan diri dengan perjanjian ini kerana dia peminat setia Harimau Malaya, dia terpaksa mengikut Chin Chye kerana ingin menghalang Rosman daripada mencuri kekasihnya Azira, yang memerlukan wang untuk pembedahan neneknya.Oleh kerana kesuntukan masa dan duit, Chin Chye dan Malik berjumpa dengan M.R. Baby, untuk mendapatkan pinjaman wang.Namun M.R. Baby pula naik marah apabila mendengar rancangan mereka untuk memberi rasuah kepada pasukan bola sepak Malaysia kerana M.R. Baby bertaruh untuk Malaysia agar menang.

programme.desc: Seorang wanita hamil pulang ke rumah keluarga datuk dan neneknya yang baru meninggal dunia untuk meluangkan masa bersama ibunya yang terasing. Apa yang bermula sebagai perjumpaan bertukar menjadi menakutkan.

programme.title: Bohsia 2: Jalan Kembali
programme.desc: Tasha adalah seorang gadis yang dibesarkan tanpa keluarga dan pendidikan, memaksanya untuk mencari perlindungan di dunia bawah tanah, di kalangan samseng jalanan. Dia tidak lama kemudian menjadi bosan dengan kehidupannya yang tidak bermakna, tetapi jalannya menuju penebusan adalah jalan yang diturap dengan banyak halangan.

programme.desc: Desta dilahirkan dalam keluarga bahagia. Namun, kebahagiaan dalam keluarga tidak kekal lama apabila hantaran sihir membawa kepada kematian kedua ibu bapa. Desta membesar menjadi seorang yang menyendiri dan penuh misteri. Keinginannya untuk membalas dendam membuatkan dia mencari dalang di sebalik kematian ibu bapanya.

Bagaimanapun, kakaknya meminta dia menyertainya dan beberapa rakan atletnya ke sebuah kampung kecil untuk memberi makanan dan mainan kepada penduduk kampung. Apa yang bermula sebagai perjalanan untuk membantu orang ramai bertukar menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila anak buah Yang tiba di kampung dan mengambil alih, menuntut pembebasan Yang atau peluru berpandu nuklear akan melanda Bangkok. Apabila penduduk kampung dibunuh kiri dan kanan, Daew dan para atlet mesti memulakan revolusi menentang kezaliman sebelum terlambat.

Dikhianati, didedahkan dan diburu oleh pembunuh paling maut dalam perniagaan, kini Natee mempunyai kod baharu. Jadi lebih pantas. Lebih kuat. Pukul lebih kuat. Bertahan.

Semasa meneroka lebih dalam ke dalam gua bawah air, gelongsor batu menghalang pintu keluar mereka, dan tidak lama kemudian mereka menemui makhluk karnivor yang lebih besar telah menambahkannya ke rantai makanannya.

Dia mula bertanya soalan dan menghantar orang barunya, Osman, menyamar untuk mengetahui apa yang sebenarnya berlaku di losmen misteri itu. Tetapi apabila Osman hilang, Fadil bergegas ke losmen untuk mencarinya, hanya untuk melencong apabila dia melihat sesosok bayangan gelap di jalan raya di hadapannya, menyebabkan dia terbabas. Fadil sedar ada sesuatu yang lebih besar sedang bermain.

Sebelum itu Mahrub memuja pokok tersebut sambil berkata-kata dan memujuk penunggu pokok itu. Mafrub rebah mati seiring dengan pokok jejawi itu tumbang ke bumi.

programme.title: Zifir-I Azap
programme.desc: Hakan, yang ingin menjimatkan wang dan mencari wang dengan cara yang singkat, telah membuat segala cara mubah untuk permintaan ini, mempunyai cita-cita yang tidak mengenal halangan. Kesilapan yang tidak disengajakan menyebabkan nasib Hakan dan rakan-rakannya tidak diketahui. Orang muda yang pergi ke arah tujuan yang tidak mereka ketahui pergi ke pembahagian keperibadian dalam diri mereka.

programme.title: Dosa Wanita
programme.desc: Perkahwinan antara Dubas Kassim dengan Zainab tidak mendapat restu daripada ibunya, Mak Wan. Walaupun sudah memiliki seorang anak, Mak Wan masih tidak boleh menerima Zainab sebagai menantunya. Oleh sebab Dubas sering belayar ke Indonesia atas urusan kerja, rakannya Johar sering mengambil kesempatan untuk berhubung dengan Zainab sehingga hubungan itu diketahui Mak Wan. Mak Wan mengambil kesempatan untuk mengugut Zainab agar meninggalkan anak dan suaminya sekiranya dia tak mahu rahsianya terbongkar. Zainab telah dihalau oleh Mak Wan dan memisahkan Zainab daripada anaknya yang masih kecil.

programme.title: Saudagar Minyak Urat
programme.desc: Kehidupan seharian Yusof, sorang lelaki miang sering dikawal oleh isterinya. Untuk mengelakkan pertengkaran, Yusof akan berpura-pura kaku apabila isterinya itu membebel. Isterinya meminta nasihat seorang penipu untuk memastikan Yusof patuh kepada arahannya. Yusof pula bertindak balas dengan mengupah seorang bomoh untuk menundukkan isterinya. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku antara mereka berdua.

programme.title: Neracha
programme.desc: Akibat kesempitan hidup, Rahman terpaksa mencuri wang di tempat kerjanya untuk menampung kos rawatan anaknya yang sedang sakit. Dia menjadi buruan polis dan telah melarikan diri ke Pahang. Ketika berada di Pahang, Rahman telah disalah anggap sebagai Husin, adik kepada orang kaya yang menghilangkan diri kerana bergaduh dengan abangnya. Peluang keemasan ini diambil oleh Rahman untuk menyamar sebagai adik orang kaya itu, namun isteri dan anaknya masih berharap agar dia pulang dan menyerah diri kepada pihak polis.

programme.title: Pilih Menantu
programme.desc: Aziz dan Zain masing-masing bekerja sebagai pemandu dan pembantu rumah dengan seorang hartawan bernama Ahmad Nisfu. Ketika majikan tiada di rumah, mereka berdua telah mengambil kesempatan untuk menyamar sebagai anak orang kaya. Mereka berdua berkenalan dengan dua orang gadis bernama Nona dan Noni lalu jatuh cinta. Apabila Ahmad Nisfu pulang ke rumah, pelbagai kekalutan berlaku kepada Aziz dan Zain. Dapatkah mereka menutup rahsia serta berkahwin dengan Nona dan Noni?

programme.title: Kechewa
programme.desc: Rafeah, seorang penyanyi terkenal di sebuah restoran, menceritakan kisah tragis penjaga zaman kanak-kanaknya yang bertukar menjadi ibu angkatnya, Kesuma. Dalam cerita itu, Rafeah menceritakan bagaimana Kesuma datang untuk tinggal bersama keluarganya. Kehadiran Kesuma tidak disenangi oleh ibu Rafeah yang tidak berperikemanusiaan. Kerana jijik dengan cara isterinya itu, bapa Rafeah akhirnya jatuh cinta kepada Kesuma yang baik hati, namun hubungan mereka ditakdirkan penuh dengan kesukaran.

programme.title: Rasa Sayang Eh
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Baning, seorang seniman terkenal di pentas bangsawan yang menghidapi penyakit sedu. Dia tidak boleh mengawal penyakit itu sehingga sering pengsan apabila dihampiri perempuan. Baning membuat keputusan untuk mendapatkan rawatan di Kuala Lumpur. Menurut dari seorang pakar yang merawatnya, penyakitnya boleh sembuh dengan sendiri apabila dia bertemu jodoh dengan seorang perempuan. Apabila pulang ke Singapura, Baning berkenalan dengan seorang doktor wanita dan penyakitnya mulai sembuh. Namun begitu, malang pula yang menimpa dirinya apabila dia dituduh menjadi seorang pembunuh. Apakah yang akan terjadi kepada dirinya?

programme.title: Mambang Moden
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kehidupan sekumpulan anak muda yang aktif dalam seni persembahan. Anuar, seorang biduan ternama jatuh cinta dengan seorang janda muda bernama Haslin yang belajar menyanyi dengannya. Pada masa yang sama, muncul seorang lelaki misteri bernama Herman yang sering mengekori mereka berdua. Herman mengugut Haslin agar meninggalkan Anuar dan berkahwin dengannya atau rahsianya terbongkar.

programme.title: Matahari
programme.desc: Tentera Jepun mula menjajah Tanah Melayu pada tahun 1942. Keadaan bertambah parah apabila ada dalam orang kampung yang menjadi tali barut Jepun. Ramai orang kampung telah dibunuh, termasuklah penghulunya kerana enggan memberi kerjasama kepada tentera Jepun. Dalam kekalutan itu, muncul seorang gadis bernama Matahari yang memimpin sekumpulan orang kampung untuk berjuang mempertahankan tanah airnya daripada terus dijajah.

programme.title: Saudagar Minyak Urat
programme.desc: Kehidupan seharian Yusof, sorang lelaki miang sering dikawal oleh isterinya. Untuk mengelakkan pertengkaran, Yusof akan berpura-pura kaku apabila isterinya itu membebel. Isterinya meminta nasihat seorang penipu untuk memastikan Yusof patuh kepada arahannya. Yusof pula bertindak balas dengan mengupah seorang bomoh untuk menundukkan isterinya. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku antara mereka berdua.

programme.title: Mambang Moden
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kehidupan sekumpulan anak muda yang aktif dalam seni persembahan. Anuar, seorang biduan ternama jatuh cinta dengan seorang janda muda bernama Haslin yang belajar menyanyi dengannya. Pada masa yang sama, muncul seorang lelaki misteri bernama Herman yang sering mengekori mereka berdua. Herman mengugut Haslin agar meninggalkan Anuar dan berkahwin dengannya atau rahsianya terbongkar.

programme.title: Pilih Menantu
programme.desc: Aziz dan Zain masing-masing bekerja sebagai pemandu dan pembantu rumah dengan seorang hartawan bernama Ahmad Nisfu. Ketika majikan tiada di rumah, mereka berdua telah mengambil kesempatan untuk menyamar sebagai anak orang kaya. Mereka berdua berkenalan dengan dua orang gadis bernama Nona dan Noni lalu jatuh cinta. Apabila Ahmad Nisfu pulang ke rumah, pelbagai kekalutan berlaku kepada Aziz dan Zain. Dapatkah mereka menutup rahsia serta berkahwin dengan Nona dan Noni?

programme.title: Jurang Bahaya
programme.desc: Seorang penyanyi kelab malam bernama Xhiang Xhiang disyaki telah diculik. Jefri Zain dengan bantuan Ai Si pergi menyiasat ke mana hilangnya Xhiang Xhiang. Mereka mengesyaki kakak Xhiang Xhiang telah menyembunyikan adiknya kerana dia terlibat dengan pertubuhan rahsia. Dapatkah Jefri Zain dan Ai Si merungkai segala kegiatan pertubuhan rahsia itu serta menyelamatkan Xhiang Xhiang daripada bahaya?

programme.title: Siapa Besar
programme.desc: Busu dan Hitam masing-masing tinggal berjiran di sebuah kawasan perumahan. Pada mulanya mereka hidup aman damai, namun lama kelamaan hubungan baik itu menjadi keruh akibat terlalu menurut kehendak isteri masing-masing. Busu dan Hitam terpaksa berlakon saling membenci antara satu sama lain, namun mengekalkan persahabatan di belakang isteri mereka. Tanpa disedari anak mereka pula jatuh cinta dan mencari cara bagaimana ingin mendamaikan keadaan.

programme.title: Kechewa
programme.desc: Rafeah, seorang penyanyi terkenal di sebuah restoran, menceritakan kisah tragis penjaga zaman kanak-kanaknya yang bertukar menjadi ibu angkatnya, Kesuma. Dalam cerita itu, Rafeah menceritakan bagaimana Kesuma datang untuk tinggal bersama keluarganya. Kehadiran Kesuma tidak disenangi oleh ibu Rafeah yang tidak berperikemanusiaan. Kerana jijik dengan cara isterinya itu, bapa Rafeah akhirnya jatuh cinta kepada Kesuma yang baik hati, namun hubungan mereka ditakdirkan penuh dengan kesukaran.

programme.title: Rasa Sayang Eh
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Baning, seorang seniman terkenal di pentas bangsawan yang menghidapi penyakit sedu. Dia tidak boleh mengawal penyakit itu sehingga sering pengsan apabila dihampiri perempuan. Baning membuat keputusan untuk mendapatkan rawatan di Kuala Lumpur. Menurut dari seorang pakar yang merawatnya, penyakitnya boleh sembuh dengan sendiri apabila dia bertemu jodoh dengan seorang perempuan. Apabila pulang ke Singapura, Baning berkenalan dengan seorang doktor wanita dan penyakitnya mulai sembuh. Namun begitu, malang pula yang menimpa dirinya apabila dia dituduh menjadi seorang pembunuh. Apakah yang akan terjadi kepada dirinya?

programme.title: Masuk Angin Keluar Asap
programme.desc: Wahid, seorang naib penghulu di sebuah kampung dicintai seorang wanita kaya bernama Aini, namun dia tidak mencintai wanita itu. Pada suatu hari, Wahid telah membuat dua orang kaya: Mak Siti dan Pak Rahman bergaduh akibat perselisihan faham. Dalam masa yang sama, anak Mak Siti bernama Yusof telah lama menjalinkan hubungan dengan anak dara Pak Rahman bernama Fatimah. Pak Rahman ingin mengahwinkan anaknya dengan Wahid dan menolak pinangan Yusof. Setelah pinangannya ditolak, Yusof membawa lari Fatimah untuk bernikah di rumah imam.

programme.title: Ribut
programme.desc: Seorang hartawan di sebuah kampung bernama Ismail adalah lelaki yang bermata keranjang. Dia suka mengambil anak-anak gadis kampung untuk dijadikan isterinya dengan bantuan Yusof. Pada suatu hari, dia ternampak seorang gadis bernama Minah lalu ingin berkahwin dengannya. Perkara ini tidak disenangi Husin, kekasih Minah. Ismail melihat Husin sebagai batu penghalang pada kehendaknya, lalu dia merancang sesuatu untuk menyingkirkan Husin daripada kampung itu.

programme.title: Neracha
programme.desc: Akibat kesempitan hidup, Rahman terpaksa mencuri wang di tempat kerjanya untuk menampung kos rawatan anaknya yang sedang sakit. Dia menjadi buruan polis dan telah melarikan diri ke Pahang. Ketika berada di Pahang, Rahman telah disalah anggap sebagai Husin, adik kepada orang kaya yang menghilangkan diri kerana bergaduh dengan abangnya. Peluang keemasan ini diambil oleh Rahman untuk menyamar sebagai adik orang kaya itu, namun isteri dan anaknya masih berharap agar dia pulang dan menyerah diri kepada pihak polis.

programme.title: Matahari

programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Walker Fun Kaohsiung (M) Ep214215
programme.desc: Walker Fun Kaohsiung is a travel reality show that takes viewers on an exciting journey through the vibrant city of Kaohsiung. With 35 different routes, the show explores the citys hidden gems, local culture, and unique experiences. From bustling night markets to serene temples, Walker Fun Kaohsiung showcases the best of Kaohsiung.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep18
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep299300
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Top Singers (T) Ep629
programme.desc: The show 'Top Singers' aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep954
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: My Hero, My Daddy (M) Ep2930
programme.desc: A fathers love for his daughters landed Jinfa Huang in battles against other men right within his family, as he found himself in conflict with his sons-in-law. His 3 daughters each possessed a distinct personality but were similarly headstrong and in romantic relationships that caused their fathers brows to crease. Tianlan, his eldest, was in love with Minglu Xu, Jinfas superior who never missed an opportunity to make life difficult for him; Tianhong, his second daughter, was drifting apart from him because of her husband; meanwhile, his youngest girl was challenging the taboo of a campus romance. How would Jinfa emerge victor in this fight to protect the 3 loves of his life?

programme.title: The Monkey King 3
programme.desc: Monkey King, Pigsy and Sandy escort Monk Tang to retrieve the scriptures and accidentally head into the mysterious Female Kingdom. The Queen falls in love with Monk Tang at first sight, but her advisor orders Monk Tang and his disciples to be executed. As the four attract the appearance of River Spirit, the Female Kingdom is plunged into crisis!

programme.title: My Wife is a Gambling Maestro
programme.desc: Natalie Yao Meng stars as the gambling queen, Ying Ying, who is a contender for the Asian God of Gamblers competition. But before the competition she is betrayed by her fianc and left for dead. Rescued by a young man called Gerrard (Nick Cheung) but suffering from amnesia, Ying Ying, must recover in time to compete in the big event!

programme.title: Ip Man 3
programme.desc: When some gangsters led by a ruthless American property developer force a school to sell their land, Ip Man fights to protect it. Subsequently, Ip Man is challenged by another Wing Chun master Zhang Tian Zhi for the Grandmaster title. Ip Man accepts the challenge for the sake of his family and disciples, and wins the duel for the title.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: The Lady Improper
programme.desc: Siu Man is divorced by her husband due to her fear of intimacy. After that, she wants to restart her life by taking over her fathers restaurant. Siu Man hires a new chef with unique culinary philosophy that revitalizes her. Tired of the shackles she placed on herself, Siu Man embarks on a journey of self-discovery and sexual liberation.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Chois actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: Come Back Home
programme.desc: In a chilly winter, De and his family goes on a self-drive tour to Changbai Mountain. The holiday turns tragic when Des eight-year-old son goes missing. He seeks help from the local police but is unable to find his son. Though the golden hour has passed, De and the rescue team insist on continuing the search. Can they finally rescue the boy?

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earths surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: Time Still Turns the Pages
programme.desc: High school teacher Cheng recalls his violent childhood memories when he finds an anonymous suicide note in the classroom. While he has to prevent the tragedy involving a suicidal student from happening, he also has to face a series of family problems with his wife wanting to divorce him and his fathers serious illness.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: Red Line
programme.desc: A former professional car racer, Le falls into despair after causing his brother's death in a car race, until he meets female doctor Hui and becomes an ambulance driver who vows to save lives with speed. Meanwhile, the truth about his brothers accident emerges with the investigation of Le's three good friends...

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kits master, Debo.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: The Lady Iron Chef
programme.desc: Beer girl and part-time model Ceci has terrible cooking skills. Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown

programme.title: Last Suspect
programme.desc: Lawyer Chen receives a mysterious call demanding her to defend a murder suspect after her daughter is kidnapped, and is told that she can only save her daughter by winning the case. As she starts investigation with the police and evidence emerges, Chen discovers the truth and reveals the mastermind. Can she rescue her daughter in time?

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Shining for One Thing
programme.desc: Zhang Wan Sen plans to confess his crush on Lin Bei Xing after the college entrance exam, but an accident changes everything tragically. As Zhang feels helpless and devastated, he fortuitously travels back in time with Lin Bei Xing before the accident happens. Can he make amends and convey his regrets this time?

programme.title: The Monkey King
programme.desc: After Goddess Nuwa sacrifices herself to save the mortal world, Monkey King comes into being from one of her crystals. Powerful and uncontrollable, Monkey King challenges the Jade Emperor and causes an uproar in heaven, unwittingly creating an opportunity for the wicked Buffalo Demon King to wage war in heaven.

programme.title: The Flying Guillotine
programme.desc: Ma Teng is an assassin of the Flying Guillotine Squad, a group of killers commissioned by the Emperor Yung. When Ma starts to question the morality of his missions, he finds himself becoming a fugitive hunted by his former comrades.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: The Silent Swordsman
programme.desc: This is adapted from Louis Chas The Book and the Sword. A young swordsman is tasked to lead a patriotic secret society to fight the traitorous general who colludes with the enemy. At the same time, he encounters a female warrior and two beautiful princesses, and is caught between all their affections for him.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: Tales Of A Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chan's long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: My Young Auntie
programme.desc: An elderly landowner marries young Dai Nan to keep his inheritance away from his unscrupulous nephew before he dies. When Dai Nan brings along the deed to meet his other nephew, a series of amusing incidents happen with this young auntie, the nephew and his son. Kara Hui won Best Actress in the first Hong Kong Film Awards for her role as Dai Nan.

programme.title: The Grand Substitution
programme.desc: In this Opera epic, a loyal Imperial Court servant gives up his own newborn son to save the prince from an evil official.

programme.title: Heroes Shed No Tears
programme.desc: Kao Chien Fei is a young swordsman who wields a special sword with a teardrop marked on its blade. He is charged with averting an impending crisis in the martial arts world, but the villain, Zhou Tung Lai, wishes to become the ruler in the martial arts world, and launches a scheme to pit the various heroes against one another.

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: The Heroic Ones
programme.desc: The story is set in the Tang Dynasty and David Chiang plays the 13th Prince, a powerful fighter whose prestigious status provokes jealously, leading to a gruesome family feud.

programme.title: Lovers Blades
programme.desc: The Lovers Blades, a pair of invincible weapons, are to be delivered to the Qing Emperor. However, they accidentally fell into the hands of Xiao Zhong Hui and Yuan Guan Nan, so Imperial Chief Zhuo Tian Xiong hunts them down for the blades. As the battle begins, the secret of the blades are also revealed.

programme.title: Vengeance Of A Snow Girl
programme.desc: A crippled woman seeks vengeance against the four men who killed her parents. However, when she crosses path with a young warrior who falls in love with her, trouble ensues as his father is one of the killers responsible for her family's massacre years ago.

programme.title: The House Of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: Shaolin Hand Lock
programme.desc: Li Cheng Yings father was set up and killed by his old friend Ling Hao. Li, who has learnt Shaolin Hand Lock from his father, is on a mission to avenge his death. He works as an undercover guard at Lings house where he meets his long-lost brother, and the two team up to take revenge for their father against Ling.

programme.title: Song Of Orchid Island
programme.desc: Dr. He moves to the remote Lanyu island off the coast of Taiwan to look for his long lost father, and starts to run a clinic curing islanders who are bitten by the fatal red worms there. He meets Ya Lan who works as a nurse in his clinic and falls in love with him. Things get vicious for Dr. He as a jealous islander plots to get rid of him

programme.title: The Silver Fox
programme.desc: The formidable swordswoman Silver Fox was a child when her father was senselessly wounded by his step brother, and her mother raped. It is payback time eighteen years later, as her father trains her up with kung fu to take revenge on his behalf.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: Chinatown Kid
programme.desc: After getting into trouble with a local gangster, Chui Ho, a young man, Tam Dong flees to San Francisco and manages to get a job in a restaurant in Chinatown. Tam Dong finds himself embroiled with the gang again while in San Francisco, and has to fight Chui Ho when the two meet again...

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxus enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: The Winged Tiger
programme.desc: If the two big villains Winged Tiger and Underworld King join forces, the martial arts world will be plunged into chaos. This evil union is set to occur with the marriage of the Underworld Kings sister and the Winged Tiger. Can this dangerous duo be stopped before one says "I do"?

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: Hex After Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung And The Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung meets a famous courtesan in Suzhou and in order to spend as much time as possible with her, he builds a direct underground tunnel into the Forbidden City. The emperors sudden appearances through this direct access shock his people but it is also at this time that he helps the needy and cracks the gambling business in Suzhou.

programme.title: The Kung-Fu Instructor
programme.desc: Wong Yang is a famous martial artist who is forced to teach kung fu to the Mong Clan, an evil clan which is trying to destroy its nemesis, the Chow Clan. Chow Ping from the Chow Clan is a student of Wongs caught in the Mongs territory and as punishment, the Mong Clan wants to cut off Chow Pings limbs. Wong steps in to defend his student.

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: The Eight Diagram Pole Fighter
programme.desc: The Yang Generals were ambushed by the enemies and only two of the sons survived. The fifth son of Yangs escapes to Shaolin temple and learns the pole-fighting techniques from the monks, eventually creating his own Eight Diagram Pole Fight and teaming up with the Shaolin monks to avenge his family.

programme.title: The Twin Bracelets
programme.desc: Two teenage girls make a pledge to look after each other in a small Chinese fishing town, where the notions of women's rights or sexual freedom are absent. One ends up happily married to a stranger, while the other is cruelly betrothed to the abusive son of a wealthy family and has to seek to free herself from the situation.

programme.title: Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A Wu Dang disciple Fu, kills the chief of Wu Dang Clan and frames it on the chiefs illegitimate child, Yun. Fu then proclaims himself the new chief and orders the killing of Yun, who vows to avenge his fathers death and learns the invincible silkworm martial arts style in order to defeat Fu.

programme.title: Diary Of A Lady-Killer
programme.desc: Tycoon Zhou is a playboy who is engaged to be married, but that did not keep him from working his charms on as many ladies as he can. He keeps a diary about his romantic escapades and soon, the women with whom he has been intimate with are being murdered one by one. Zhou becomes the number one suspect by the police but is the killer someone else?

programme.title: Vengeance Is A Golden Blade
programme.desc: Convoy Master Lis wife has an affair with his rival Long, who plans to steal Lis Golden Blade and kill him as well as his young daughter. Li and his daughter manage to escape and the latter grows up to be a skilled swordswoman who vows to avenge her mothers death a lie told by Li. The truth is revealed when she sees her mother alive by chance.

programme.title: The Mirror And The Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: The Golden Buddha
programme.desc: A map indicating the location of the Chans family heirloom is hidden in three Golden Buddha statues. Paul, an insurance agent, finds one statue by chance and Chans daughter has another one. This makes them targets of treasure-hunting criminals and they have to team up to defeat them before unveiling the hidden secrets.

programme.title: This Is Where I Leave You
programme.desc: When their father passes away, four grown siblings (Jason Bateman, Tina Fey, Adam Driver, Corey Stoll), bruised and banged up by their respective adult lives, are forced to return to their childhood home and live under the same roof together for a week, along with their over-sharing mother (Jane Fonda) and an assortment of spouses, exes and might-have-beens. Confronting their history and the frayed states of their relationships among the people who know and love them best, they ultimately reconnect in hysterical and emotionally affecting ways amid the chaos, humor, heartache and redemption that only families can provide-- driving us insane even as they remind us of our truest, and often best, selves. Comedy director Shawn Levy (Date Night)helms the hilarious script by Jonathan Tropper based on his own best-selling novel.

Hero is a word we often hear in the world of sports, but heroism is not always about achievements on the field of play. 42 tells the story of two men -- the great Jackie Robinson (Chadwick Boseman) and the legendary Brooklyn Dodgers manager Branch Rickey (Harrison Ford) -- whose brave stand against prejudice forever changed the world by changing the game of baseball. In 1946, Rickey signed Robinson to the team, breaking Major League Baseball's infamous color line. Facing racism from every side, Robinson demonstrated tremendous courage by letting his talent on the field do the talking -- ultimately winning over fans and his teammates, and paving the way for others to follow.

Tiny Flea tells Lion that if he dares to enter the Great Cave of Tinga Tinga then maybe he will find his roar. Lion plucks up courage and goes into the Great Cave. He roars with all his might, but a bigger roar comes back! Lion stands strong. He roars again and an even bigger roar comes back. Lion's very own Echo! He has found his roar! programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep24
programme.desc: Why Zebra Has Stripes - Zebra was once very easy to spot in Tinga Tinga as he was bright white all over. This very annoying as all he wanted was to be left alone to munch on yummy grass and get fat. One day, Eagle arrives at the Watering Hole with a new pair of sharp talons saying that she found them in the Great Cave. The animals excitedly rush to find something for themselves. Zebra accompanies Tortoise and the Monkeys into the Cave where they discover the last remaining item; a plain black coat. The Monkeys persuade Zebra to try it on. By holding in his stomach, Zebra manages to get the coat on but it is extremely tight and the black coat starts to rip. In fact, the more Zebra eats the more the coat rips until Zebra has a stripy black and white coat which he is extremely proud of. Not only that, his new stripes make him very difficult to spot amongst the tall grasses of the plains. Finally, Zebra can eat as much grass as he likes and not be spotted by the other animals!

programme.title: Kronologi Zayn Rayyan (New)
programme.desc: Bernama TV menerbitkan Augmented reality (AR) kes kematian kanak-kanak autisme, Zayn Rayyan Abdul Matiin, 6, yang dibunuh pada Disember 2023 di Damansara Damai, Selangor. AR ini menceritakan kronologi dari mula kejadian ini berlaku sehingga kepada penahanan kedua ibu bapa Zayn Rayyan pada 31 Mei 2024. Setelah ditahan reman 13 hari, Zaim Ikhwan Zahari dan Ismanira Abdul Manaf yang kedua-duanya berumur 29 tahun menghadapi pertuduhan mengabaikan kanak-kanak berkenaan dengan cara kemungkinan menyebabkan kecederaan fizikal terhadapnya. Pasangan itu mengaku tidak bersalah selepas pertuduhan terhadap mereka dibacakan dan minta dibicarakan. Mahkamah menetapkan 26 Julai 2024 sebagai tarikh sebutan semula kes. Bagaimanapun, kes pembunuhan ini telah menimbulkan pelbagai pendapat dan spekulasi daripada orang awam yang masih menunggu agar pelaku sebenar ditangkap dan menerima pengadilan di mahkamah.
